textContent:
---ang mga ganap---

Okay it's been a while since I last wrote an entry, pero pano ba naman kase ang dami pangyayari HAHAHAHAH. tas sunod sunod pa, tas nakakastress pa iba. Jusq. Pero thankful talaga ko kasama ko bbycakes ko huhu

---yie love mo ko---

Nabangga ako for the first time this month and j.christ it was so traumatizing. Oo, things turned out well in the end pero still, it forever left a mark on me kaya may PTSD na talaga ako sa mga truck HAHAHAHAHA. Pero i just want you to know how thankful I am na all throughout the experience, andon ka. I really felt how much you love me that day. I really felt how much you care about me. Jusq ba naman, napag commute ko ba naman yung bbycakes ko HUHUHUHU. Tas andon pa parents mo oh ha. Full support talagaaaa. 

I love you so much Rei!! I'm so grateful I met you! I always thank God in my prayers na nakilala kita. And I promise I'll do everything I can in order to pay it back, kase you really do deserve the best. I promise na I'll always be there for you pag kailangan mo ko. Hinding hindi kita papabayaan.

---new friends---

Nagkita tayo ng friends mo last weekend, nagkaraoke pa nga HAHAHAHAHA. I really have fun with them and I'm really thankful na pinakilala mo ko sa kanila HAHAHAHAH. I keep on saying na naubusan nako ng kaibigan pero dahil sayo, yay, may bago nako ulit HAHAHAHAHA. I really do look forward to meeting them again ket na drained na drained battery ko lagi kase ang ingay ko pag kasama sila BWAHAHAHAHA.
